graph TB
    subgraph "Model Registry Operator"
        Controller[Controller Manager]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        Metrics[Metrics Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        Health[Health Endpoints<br/>8081/TCP HTTP]

        Controller -->|validates/mutates| Webhook
        Controller -->|exposes| Metrics
        Controller -->|exposes| Health
    end

    subgraph "Model Registry Deployment (Created by Operator)"
        REST[Model Registry REST API<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS]
        gRPC[Model Registry gRPC API<br/>9090/TCP gRPC]
        REST -.->|same pod| gRPC
    end

    User[User/Admin] -->|creates| ModelRegistryCR[ModelRegistry CR]
    ModelRegistryCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates| Deployment[Model Registry Deployment]
    Controller -->|creates| Services[Services<br/>REST & gRPC]
    Controller -->|creates| Routes[OpenShift Routes]
    Controller -->|creates| IstioResources[Istio Gateway<br/>VirtualService<br/>DestinationRule]
    Controller -->|creates| AuthResources[AuthorizationPolicy<br/>AuthConfig]
    Controller -->|creates| RBAC[Roles & RoleBindings]

    Deployment -->|contains| REST
    Deployment -->|contains| gRPC

    REST -->|connects to| Database[(PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>5432/3306 TCP)]
    gRPC -->|connects to| Database

    Controller -->|depends on| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    REST -.->|optional| Istio[Istio Service Mesh<br/>mTLS]
    gRPC -.->|optional| Istio
    REST -.->|optional| Authorino[Authorino<br/>50051/TCP gRPC]

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Metrics fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style REST fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style gRPC fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelRegistryCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Database fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Istio fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Authorino fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
